&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own global content and safety enforcement end to end policy enforcement, misuse detection and response, case resolution, and escalation protocols.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Act as the senior escalation point and incident lead for complex safety, integrity, reputational, and operational issues.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build internal governance and risk frameworks for AI safety, content moderation, and platform integrity, partnering with Product, Engineering, Legal, Security, Policy, and Operations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as operational lead for GDPR and broader regulatory compliance (EU AI Act, Digital Services Act), and support the relationship with the Irish Data Protection Commission as our lead EU supervisory authority.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Direct how Inflection AI processes EU personal data, setting the purposes and means in coordination with the Ireland-based board and U.S. leadership.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and maintain the Irish entity&#39;s compliance documentation: records of processing activities, data protection impact assessments, and privacy policies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help stand up and scale Inflection AI&#39;s Ireland office&amp;nbsp; recruiting and onboarding the local team, and partnering with Legal, outside counsel, and local regulators to keep the Irish entity fully operational and in good standing.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
